Arizona-bound senior to 4-1 last week after striking out nine in an 8-2 victory 
over Simi Valley Royal. . . . The Whittier Christian boys' volleyball team saw 
its 47-match winning streak broken last Tuesday in a four-set loss to Santa Ana 
Calvary Chapel. Times' Top 20 Baseball Poll 
