narrating? . . . The county's Homeless Issues Task Force is counting on just 
that. "It Was a Wonderful Life," plays at the Trinity Episcopal Church in 
Orange at that price tonight at 7. Foster chronicles the lives of six former 
middle-class women who wound up homeless. Your money goes toward helping the 
Martha House, a homeless women's shelter in Orange. 
