<HEADLINE>
<P>
EL DORADO'S SWEET GOING TO FRESNO PACIFIC 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Jamie Sweet, a three-time all-Empire League player for the El Dorado girls' 
basketball team, has signed a letter of intent to play at Fresno Pacific, an 
NAIA school. Sweet, a 5-foot-9 guard, averaged 9.6 points for the Golden Hawks. 
</P>
</TEXT>
