<P>
LACK OF TRUST 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Let me express how much I appreciate Ventura City Councilman Jim Monahan's 
"Father Knows Best" attitude toward the residents of Ventura County. 
</P>
<P>
 He has no faith on our advisory vote (on a water desalination plant) as we 
"were confused on what we were voting on."Isn't it nice to have our elected 
officials listen and have trust in our intelligence? 
</P>
<P>
 But, since "there was a lot of misinformation circulating during the 
