REGIONAL EARNINGS: ON ASSIGNMENT POSTS PROFIT IN 1ST QUARTER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 On Assignment Inc., the Calabasas provider of temporary professional workers, 
said its first-quarter profit was $643,000, up 23% from $521,000 in the same 
quarter a year earlier.For the three months that ended March 31, the company's 
revenue increased 16% to $10.34 million from $8.90 million the previous year. 
</P>
<P>
 The company attributed the gain to increased sales and expense controls. Also, 
the company has started a new division that provides temporary workers for 
banking and finance companies. 
