<DOCNO> LA042694-0279 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 036065 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
April 26, 1994, Tuesday, Home Edition 
