</P>
<P>
 Traffic Patterns: Police say some streets around the library will be closed at 
11 a.m. Wednesday. Where you will not be able to drive: 
</P>
<P>
 3. Public Viewing Today 
</P>
<P>
 The body of Nixon, in a closed casket, will lie in state beginning at 3 p.m. 
today. Public viewing will continue until 11 a.m. Wednesday. 
</P>
