36 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Boys' basketball -- A story in Monday's edition failed to include Tony 
Gonzalez from Huntington Beach High as a first-team all-county player honored 
at The Times Orange County's basketball awards breakfast Sunday. 
</P>
