</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Arts budget -- Friday's Morning Report incorrectly indicated that a state 
Senate subcommittee has recommended elimination of the California Arts Council 
budget. Although the budget has been targeted for elimination in the past, the 
CAC this year has been asked to present the Senate subcommittee with 
information from an internal economic impact study. The subcommittee is 
scheduled to review that information on Wednesday before taking any action. 
</P>
