<HEADLINE>
<P>
THE TIMES 100 / THE BEST PERFORMING COMPANIES IN AMERICA; EDITOR'S NOTE: 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 This is the seventh edition of our annual guide to the best and biggest in 
California business.The section takes its name from our ranking of companies by 
return on equity, a list we call The Times 100. We also rank firms by sales, 
growth, market value, employment and a host of other factors which together 
make up a report card on California companies during 1993. Star Services, 2201 
Third Street, San Francisco, CA 94107 (415) 864-8706 EDITOR: David R. Olmos 
NEWS EDITOR: R. Paul Zieke ART DIRECTOR: Dianna Shantic ILLUSTRATIONS: Barton 
Stabler COPY EDITOR: Bob Baker, Bob Beamesderfer, Linda Beaty, Laura Dominick, 
Jean Gilbert Hawkins, Eileen Heyes, Jim Hollander, Jim Houston, Catherine 
Jordan, Bob Lynch, Marty Rossman. 
</P>
